snippet.title: BONUS: Amber Interviews Paul Prescod, Candidate for PA Senate | Chapo Trap House
snippet.description:
buy our book: http://www.chapotraphouse.com/book 
http://www.soundcloud.com/chapo-trap-house 
http://patreon.com/chapotraphouse


Amber talks to Paul Prescod, who is running for Pennsylvania State Senate in the 8th district. They discuss campaigning for labor support, working with unions towards a green future, taxing frackers & more.

Check out Paul’s campaign here: https://www.paulprescod.com/

#chapotraphouse #chapo
